  </entry>
  
  <entry>
    <title></title>
    <link href="https://roverkai.github.io/2025/10/25/Joyagentdata-agent%EF%BC%88%E8%88%92%E6%9C%8D%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%89%88%EF%BC%89/"/>
    <id>https://roverkai.github.io/2025/10/25/Joyagentdata-agent%EF%BC%88%E8%88%92%E6%9C%8D%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%89%88%EF%BC%89/</id>
    <published>2025-10-25T07:05:14.755Z</published>
    <updated>2025-10-28T07:05:39.552Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Joyagent-data-agent（舒服学习版）"><a href="#Joyagent-data-agent（舒服学习版）" class="headerlink" title="Joyagent:data-agent（舒服学习版）"></a>Joyagent:data-agent（舒服学习版）</h1><h2 id="智能问数：-data-chatQuery"><a href="#智能问数：-data-chatQuery" class="headerlink" title="智能问数： &#x2F;data&#x2F;chatQuery"></a>智能问数： &#x2F;data&#x2F;chatQuery</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> SseEmitter <span class="title function_">webChatQueryData</span><span class="params">(DataAgentChatReq req)</span> <span class="keyword">throws</span> Exception &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">SseEmitter</span> <span class="variable">emitter</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">SseEmitter</span>(AUTO_AGENT_SSE_TIMEOUT);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 获取NL2SQL请求</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">NL2SQLReq</span> <span class="variable">baseNl2SqlReq</span> <span class="operator">=</span> getBaseNl2SqlReq(req.getContent());</span><br><span class="line">    baseNl2SqlReq.setRequestId(UUID.randomUUID().toString());</span><br><span class="line">    baseNl2SqlReq.setTraceId(baseNl2SqlReq.getRequestId());</span><br><span class="line">    baseNl2SqlReq.setDbType(dataAgentConfig.getDbConfig().getType());</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 发送状态消息</span></span><br><span class="line">    enrichNl2Sql(baseNl2SqlReq);</span><br><span class="line">    emitter.send(ChatDataMessage.ofStatus(EventTypeEnum.DEBUG.name(), baseNl2SqlReq.getRequestId()));</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 执行NL2SQL</span></span><br><span class="line">    ThreadUtil.execute(() -&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            List&lt;ChatQueryData&gt; result = nl2SqlService.runNL2SQLSse(baseNl2SqlReq, emitter);</span><br><span class="line">            emitter.send(ChatDataMessage.ofData(result));</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">catch</span> (Exception e) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            log.error(<span class="string">&quot;&#123;&#125;,&#123;&#125; 智能问数异常：&#123;&#125;&quot;</span>, baseNl2SqlReq.getTraceId(), baseNl2SqlReq.getRequestId(), e.getMessage(), e);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                emitter.send(ChatDataMessage.ofError(e.getMessage()));</span><br><span class="line">            &#125; <span class="keyword">catch</span> (IOException ex) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                log.warn(<span class="string">&quot;&#123;&#125;,&#123;&#125; sse 发送异常：&#123;&#125;&quot;</span>, baseNl2SqlReq.getTraceId(), baseNl2SqlReq.getRequestId(), e.getMessage(), e);</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">finally</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                emitter.send(ChatDataMessage.ofReady(<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>));</span><br><span class="line">            &#125; <span class="keyword">catch</span> (IOException e) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                log.warn(<span class="string">&quot;&#123;&#125;,&#123;&#125; sse 发送异常：&#123;&#125;&quot;</span>, baseNl2SqlReq.getTraceId(), baseNl2SqlReq.getRequestId(), e.getMessage(), e);</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            emitter.complete();</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> emitter;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>核心功能： getBaseNl2SqlReq()</p><h2 id="其他模式：-web-api-v1-gpt-queryAgentStreamIncr"><a href="#其他模式：-web-api-v1-gpt-queryAgentStreamIncr" class="headerlink" title="其他模式： &#x2F;web&#x2F;api&#x2F;v1&#x2F;gpt&#x2F;queryAgentStreamIncr"></a>其他模式： &#x2F;web&#x2F;api&#x2F;v1&#x2F;gpt&#x2F;queryAgentStreamIncr</h2>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h1 id=&quot;Joyagent-data-agent（舒服学习版）&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#Joyagent-data-agent（舒服学习版）&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;Joyagent:data-agent（舒服学习版）&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Joyagent</summary>
      
    
    
    
    
