    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ol><li><p>标准参数（Standard Options）：</p><figure class="highlight diff"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-verbose</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-classpath</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-version</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-help</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>非标准扩展参数(Non-Standard, Extended Options):</p><figure class="highlight diff"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-Xms//memory start</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-Xmx//memory max</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-Xmn//memory new</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-Xss//stack size</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-Xloggc//log garbage collector 设置log位置</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>前缀：<code>-X</code></p></li><li><p>非稳定、高级、实验性调优参数（Non-Standard, Non-Stable）</p><figure class="highlight diff"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-XX:NewSize</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-XX:MaxNewSize</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-XX:+UseG1GC</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-XX:SurvivorRatio</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-XX:MaxTenuringThreshold</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-XX:+PrintGC//打印GC日志</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-XX:+PrintGCDetails</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-XX:+PrintGCDateStamps</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-XX:+PrintGCTimeStamps//打印从JVM启动到当前的时间</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-XX:+PrintHeapAtGC//打印每次GC前后堆状态</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-XX:+PrintTenuringDistribution //打印年龄分布</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="deletion">-XX:+PrintReferenceGC//打印软、弱、虚引用回收情况</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>前缀：<code>-XX</code></p></li></ol><p><a href="https://javaguide.cn/java/jvm/jvm-parameters-intro.html#%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E6%B0%B8%E4%B9%85%E4%BB%A3-%E5%85%83%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F-permgen-metaspace">JVM参数设置总结</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
