  <entry>
    <title>Joyagent项目启动文档</title>
    <link href="https://roverkai.github.io/2025/10/17/Joyagent%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3/"/>
    <id>https://roverkai.github.io/2025/10/17/Joyagent%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3/</id>
    <published>2025-10-17T05:56:16.000Z</published>
    <updated>2025-10-17T09:16:42.203Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>项目地址: <a href="https://github.com/jd-opensource/joyagent-jdgenie/tree/data_agent">https://github.com/jd-opensource/joyagent-jdgenie/tree/data_agent</a></p><h3 id="运行环境"><a href="#运行环境" class="headerlink" title="运行环境:"></a>运行环境:</h3><ul><li>操作系统: Linux Mint 22.1</li><li>JDK版本: 17.0.16</li><li>Maven版本: 3.9.11</li><li>Node.js版本: v22.17.1</li><li>Pnpm: 7.33.1</li><li>python版本: 3.11</li></ul><h3 id="准备阶段"><a href="#准备阶段" class="headerlink" title="准备阶段:"></a>准备阶段:</h3><ol><li><p>安装Java</p></li><li><p>安装Maven: <a href="https://dlcdn.apache.org/maven/maven-3/3.9.11/binaries/apache-maven-3.9.11-bin.tar.gz">https://dlcdn.apache.org/maven/maven-3/3.9.11/binaries/apache-maven-3.9.11-bin.tar.gz</a></p></li><li><p>安装Node: <a href="https://nodejs.org/en/download">https://nodejs.org/en/download</a></p></li><li><p>安装pnpm: </p></li><li><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ node --version</span><br><span class="line">v22.17.1 <span class="comment">#安装成功会出现版本号</span></span><br><span class="line">$ npm install -g pnpm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>python安装: <a href="https://www.python.org/downloads/">https://www.python.org/downloads/</a></p></li><li><p>注册<a href="https://platform.deepseek.com/usage">deepseek开放平台</a>(提供大模型服务)</p></li><li><p>注册<a href="https://serper.dev/">serper</a>(提供搜索服务)</p></li><li><p>克隆仓库 <code>git clone https://github.com/jd-opensource/joyagent-jdgenie.git</code></p></li></ol><h3 id="启动项目"><a href="#启动项目" class="headerlink" title="启动项目:"></a>启动项目:</h3><ol><li><p>进入项目后执行</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sh Genie_start.sh <span class="comment">#MintOS默认使用dash作为解释器,运行脚本时会出现兼容问题,可以把sh改为bash</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>根据提示安装缺少的依赖<br><img src="/images/image-20251016204226525.png" alt="image-20251016204226525"></p></li><li><p>配置后端文件, 位于 <code>genie-backend/src/main/resources/application.yml</code></p><ul><li><p>将所有<code>&lt;input llm server here&gt;</code>替换成<code>https://api.deepseek.com/v1</code></p></li><li><p>将所有<code>&lt;input llm key here&gt;</code>替换成<a href="https://platform.deepseek.com/api_keys%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%86%E9%92%A5">https://platform.deepseek.com/api_keys创建的密钥</a></p></li><li><p>还有以下内容</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">llm:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">model:</span> <span class="string">deepseek-chat</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">max-tokens:</span> <span class="number">8192</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><p>配置工具服务文件, 位于 <code>genie-tool/.env</code></p><ul><li><p><code>OPENAI_BASE_URL=https://api.deepseek.com/v1</code></p></li><li><p><code>OPENAI_API_KEY</code>注释掉</p></li><li><p><code>DEEPSEEK_API_KEY</code>注释解开, 后面填写<a href="https://platform.deepseek.com/api_keys%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%86%E9%92%A5">https://platform.deepseek.com/api_keys创建的密钥</a></p></li><li><p><code>DEFAULT_MODEL=deepseek/deepseek-chat</code></p></li><li><p>所有 ${DEFAULT_MODEL} 也都改成deepseek&#x2F;deepseek-chat</p></li><li><p><code>SERPER_SEARCH_API_KEY</code>后面填写<a href="https://serper.dev/api-keys%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%86%E9%92%A5">https://serper.dev/api-keys页面中的密钥</a></p></li></ul></li><li><p>再次运行脚本启动</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sh Genie_start.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>启动成功<br><img src="/images/image-20251017141408829.png" alt="image-20251017141408829"></p></li></ol><p>如果出现工具服务启动失败,提示:</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ValueError: Unknown scheme <span class="keyword">for</span> proxy URL URL(<span class="string">&#x27;socks://127.0.0.1:7897/&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>请在<code>genie-tool</code>项目中下载<code>httpx[socks]</code>依赖来支持 SOCKS 代理</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> genie-tool</span><br><span class="line">$ pip3 install <span class="string">&quot;httpx[socks]&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>再次启动项目即可.</p><h3 id="进阶篇-开启智能问数功能"><a href="#进阶篇-开启智能问数功能" class="headerlink" title="进阶篇-开启智能问数功能:"></a>进阶篇-开启智能问数功能:</h3><p><img src="/home/roverkai/Desktop/blog/source/_posts/Joyagent%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3.assets/image-20251017154952118.png" alt="image-20251017154952118"></p><p>启动项目后还无法直接使用智能问数功能</p><p>控制台报错:</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">openai.BadRequestError: Error code: 400 - &#123;<span class="string">&#x27;error&#x27;</span>: &#123;<span class="string">&#x27;message&#x27;</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;Model Not Exist&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;type&#x27;</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;invalid_request_error&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;param&#x27;</span>: None, <span class="string">&#x27;code&#x27;</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;invalid_request_error&#x27;</span>&#125;&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>继续深入会发现程序请求使用的模型是gpt-4o</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">2025-10-17 15:34:47.061 | INFO     | genie_tool.tool.nl2sql:_text_to_rewrite:48 - [NL2SQL] [REWRITE] request_id=06844046-761e-48b1-85d1-feffc16a67ec rewrite模块执行完成。 model_name=gpt-4o</span><br><span class="line">2025-10-17 15:34:47.061 | INFO     | genie_tool.util.log_util:__aenter__:40 - 288513d8-32d9-433b-a5aa-86cb7ac7b130 enter ask_llm start...</span><br><span class="line">2025-10-17 15:34:47.069 | INFO     | genie_tool.util.log_util:__aenter__:40 - 288513d8-32d9-433b-a5aa-86cb7ac7b130 enter ask_llm start...</span><br><span class="line">2025-10-17 15:34:47.074 | INFO     | genie_tool.util.log_util:__aenter__:40 - 288513d8-32d9-433b-a5aa-86cb7ac7b130 enter ask_llm start...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将配置文件改为</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">NL2SQL_MODEL_NAME=deepseek/deepseek-chat</span><br><span class="line">REWRITE_MODEL_NAME=deepseek/deepseek-chat</span><br><span class="line">THINK_MODEL_NAME=deepseek/deepseek-chat</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>继续启动报错</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">httpx.HTTPStatusError: Client error <span class="string">&#x27;400 Bad Request&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">for</span> url <span class="string">&#x27;https://api.deepseek.com/beta/chat/completions&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">For more information check: https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Status/400</span><br><span class="line">litellm.llms.openai.common_utils.OpenAIError: &#123;<span class="string">&quot;error&quot;</span>:&#123;<span class="string">&quot;message&quot;</span>:<span class="string">&quot;Invalid top_p value, the valid range of top_p is (0, 1.0]&quot;</span>,<span class="string">&quot;type&quot;</span>:<span class="string">&quot;invalid_request_error&quot;</span>,<span class="string">&quot;param&quot;</span>:null,<span class="string">&quot;code&quot;</span>:<span class="string">&quot;invalid_request_error&quot;</span>&#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>返回的错误消息提示: top_p的范围不包括0，但是nl2sql.py文件中初始化top_p的值为0.0</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">NL2SQLAgent</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">__init__</span>(<span class="params">self, queue: asyncio.Queue=<span class="literal">None</span></span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 用作流式</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">self</span>.queue = queue <span class="keyword">or</span> asyncio.Queue()</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">self</span>.nl2sql_llm_name = os.getenv(<span class="string">&quot;NL2SQL_MODEL_NAME&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">self</span>.rewrite_llm_name = os.getenv(<span class="string">&quot;REWRITE_MODEL_NAME&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">self</span>.think_llm_name = os.getenv(<span class="string">&quot;THINK_MODEL_NAME&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">self</span>.default_model: <span class="built_in">str</span> = <span class="string">&quot;gpt-4.1&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">self</span>.temperature: <span class="built_in">float</span> = <span class="number">0.0</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">self</span>.top_p: <span class="built_in">float</span> = <span class="number">0.0</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>现在修改为0.1</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
